body:
I'm *Dominik Angerer*, a fullstack web- & backenddeveloper at [Netural](http://netural.com) from Austria with an eye for the detail and performance as well. If you are interested in working with me, simply write a mail or call me. I was able to collect coding experience in many different technologies during my work at [Netural](http://netural.com), [Roomle](http://roomle.com), [Wallsplash](http://wallsplashapp.com), [Lanora](http://lanora.io) and as a [freelancer](http://dominikangerer.com).

If you have any questions or you want your idea get real, I would love to discuss this on a cup of coffee kakao so feel free to contact me: [me@dominikangerer.com](mailto:me@dominikangerer.com)
